what is this:
this is a catalogue of best practices
content here is not rules, but hints and guidelines 

how to use this document:
if you come across something that you consider to be a good practice
share it with the team by adding an entry describing in complete but concise detail

====================
== Best Practices ==
====================

1) send an email blast/notification to the the team after merging in your changes

2) include your name in the source files that you write (for tracking purposes)